data.description: BACK ON MARKET DUE TO BUYERS CONTINGENT PROPERTY NOT GOING UNDER CONTRACT!!  Explore this stunning ranch-style home with an nestled in the desirable Todd Creek area. Situated on a serene cul-de-sac, this property boasts numerous features that make it a dream come true. With almost 3,000 square feet on the main floor, a finished basement, and an impressive 1.81-acre lot, this home offers an abundance of space. Step inside and be captivated by the meticulous attention to detail evident in every corner of this residence. From the exquisite flooring to the luxurious bathroom finishes, solid core doors, and custom built bar, the craftsmanship shines through. The main level showcases 10-foot ceilings, while the basement features 9-foot ceilings, adding to the grandeur of the home. The main level encompasses a well-designed office space, 3 bedrooms, and 2.5 baths. The heart of the home is the living room, strategically positioned to serve as the central gathering point. This inviting space offers a generous sitting area with a cozy gas fireplace, a dining area, and a kitchen complete with a sizable granite bar, island, and pantry. On one side of the house, you'll discover a spacious primary retreat comprised of a sizable bedroom, a lavish 5-piece en-suite bathroom featuring a soaker tub, an oversized shower with dual shower heads, a double sink vanity, and an expansive walk-in closet. On the opposite side of the main level, two additional bedrooms and a full bath provide ample accommodations. The finished basement offers additional living space, including a bar area, large family room, workout area, 3/4 bath, and an extra bedroom. The attached 3-car garage with 10-foot doors ensures plenty of room for vehicles and storage needs. The property also boasts a 1,750 sq ft workshop with two levels, equipped with a convenient half bathroom, electricity (including 220V), and hot water, along with gas plumbing. This home offers a unique blend of elegance and functionality.
